            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            体制内，这4件事你一定要烂在肚子里！          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      贝鲁                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                湖边看世界              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">湖边看世界</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">fo_gushi</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">湖边看世界，世界在湖边。聊聊体制内那些事，关注官场新生态。 关心官场就是关心自己。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.5626666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" style="font-size: 17px;height: auto !important;" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/U5fBOaXlIQnA8Dn96u8HOicZa4k3TnufrMRCb360aa5SzqLiaAr3ibjicHVUbFxlDfIp2ib7uMFkGSmojOC6fd29OkQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><br></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，不是一件容易的事情。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">你不仅要面对各种复杂的人际关系，还要应付各种棘手的问题。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">你可能会遇到很多诱惑和挑战，也可能会有很多机会和收获。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，无论你处于什么样的位置，有什么样的能力，你都要记住，有些事情不要轻易透露给别人。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这是你的底线，是你在体制内生存的法宝。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">下面大家分享一下，体制内，你一定要烂在肚子里的4件事！</span><br></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">01</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">第一件事，你的背景、关系和资源。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些是你在体制内最重要的资本，也是最敏感的话题。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">你可能有着优越的家庭背景，或者有着强大的关系网，或者有着丰富的资源渠道。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些都是你可以利用的优势，但是也是你最容易被攻击的弱点。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果你把这些东西说出来，别人可能会嫉妒你，排挤你，甚至想方设法打压你。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，你要学会低调处理这些事情，不要炫耀，不要张扬，不要招惹是非。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">只有这样，你才能保护好自己的利益，避免不必要的麻烦。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">02</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">第二件事，通过找别人办成的事情。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，很多时候，</span><span style="font-size: 17px;">你可能会遇到一些超出你能力范围的事情，或者一些需要别人帮忙的事情。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这时候，你就要懂得找人办事。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">找人办事，并不是说你要推卸责任，或者利用别人。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">而是说，你要合理分配工作，利用各方面的资源和力量，达成目标。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">找人办事，并不是一件丢人的事情，而是一种智慧和能力的体现。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，在找人办事的时候，你也要注意一些原则。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">比如说，不要随便泄露机密信息，不要违反规章制度，不要损害别人的利益和声誉等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">而且，在找人办成了事情之后，你也要及时表达感谢和回报。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">只有这样，你才能建立起良好的人际关系，让别人愿意帮助你。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">03</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">第三件事，你赚钱的方法和“门路”。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，并不意味着你就没有赚钱的机会和空间。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">相反，在体制内工作，往往会有很多赚钱的方法和“门路”。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">比如说，你可以通过投资、理财等方式来实现财富增值，你可以通过做自媒体赚钱。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些都是合法合理的赚钱方式，并没有什么不妥。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，在赚钱的过程中，你也要注意一些原则。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">比如说，不要影响正常工作，不要违反法律法规，不要损害公共利益等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">而且，在赚钱之后，你也要注意保密，不要让别人知道你的财务状况。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">因为，如果你把你的赚钱方法和“门路”说出来，别人可能会妒忌你，质疑你，甚至想方设法陷害你。</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"></span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，你要学会保持低调，不要招摇，不要引起注意。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">04</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">第四件事，你跟领导私底下的关系。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，你跟领导的关系是非常重要的。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">你的领导可能会对你的工作、晋升、待遇等方面有着很大的影响。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，你要懂得跟领导沟通、交流、合作，建立起良好的工作关系。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，在跟领导建立工作关系的同时，你也要注意一些原则。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">比如说，不要过分巴结、奉承、讨好领导，不要违背自己的原则和底线，不要损害同事和团队的利益和氛围等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">而且，在跟领导建立了良好的工作关系之后，你也要注意保密，不要让别人知道你跟领导私底下的关系。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">因为，如果你把你跟领导私底下的关系说出来，别人可能会误解你，嫉妒你，甚至想方设法破坏你跟领导的关系，甚至给领导带来麻烦。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，你要学会保持谨慎，不要张扬，不要招惹是非。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">总之，在体制内工作，有很多事情是不能轻易说出口的。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些事情，就是你在体制内生存的秘密武器。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">只有把这些事情烂在肚子里，才能保证自己的安全和利益。</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="123793990" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
